headline: Assurant Q4 Earnings & Revenues Beat Estimates on Higher Premiums
summary: AIZ's Q4 results reflect higher adjusted EBITDA, solid performance in both segments, and growth in Global Automotive within Global Lifestyle.

headline: The Top 5 Analyst Questions From Everest Group’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: Everest Group’s fourth quarter was marked by a negative market reaction, as the company’s revenue and non-GAAP profit missed Wall Street expectations. Management attributed the underperformance primarily to the impact of the commercial retail business divestiture and deliberate reductions in U.S. casualty lines.
